Directions
Directions from Fort Lauderdale
Follow I-595 W
Use the 2nd from the left lane to take the exit toward Naples I-75 N
Take I-75 N for 30.9 mi
Take exit 49 for Snake Road/Big Cypress Indian Reservation
Continue on Snake Rd/ Josie Billie Hwy to Halls Rd for 25 min (18.1 mi)
Turn right onto Halls Rd
Turn left to stay on Halls Rd
Directions from Naples
Follow I-75 S for 45 min (55.0 mi)
Take exit 49 for Snake Rd/ Big Cypress Indian Reservation
Continue on Snake Rd/ Josie Billie Hwy to Halls Rd in for 25 min (18.3 mi)
Turn right onto Halls Rd
Turn left to stay on Halls Rd
